    <h1>Copy.ai Review 2026: Is It the Best AI Writing Tool?</h1>

    <p class="excerpt">We tested Copy.ai for 2 weeks on real marketing projects. Here's our honest take — the good, the bad, and whether it's worth your money.</p>

    <div class="affiliate-box">
