    <h2>What Is Copy.ai?</h2>
    <p>Copy.ai is an AI-powered writing tool that helps you create marketing copy, blog posts, social media content, emails, and more. It uses GPT-4 and other large language models to generate human-like text based on your prompts.</p>
    <p>Founded in 2020, Copy.ai has grown to over <strong>15 million users</strong> worldwide, making it one of the most popular AI writing tools on the market. But popularity doesn't always mean quality — so we put it to the test.</p>

    <h2>Our Testing Process</h2>
    <p>We used Copy.ai for 2 full weeks on real projects:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>10 blog post drafts (1,000–2,000 words each)</li>
      <li>20 social media posts (Instagram, LinkedIn, Twitter)</li>
      <li>15 email subject lines and body copies</li>
      <li>5 product descriptions for an e-commerce store</li>
      <li>3 full landing page copies</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Every output was compared against <a href="/comparisons">other AI writing tools</a> we've tested.</p>

    <h2>Key Features</h2>

    <h3>1. 90+ Content Templates</h3>
    <p>Copy.ai offers over 90 pre-built templates for different content types. Need a blog intro? There's a template. Instagram caption? Template. Cold email? Template. The variety is impressive and covers most marketing use cases.</p>

    <h3>2. Blog Post Wizard</h3>
    <p>The Blog Post Wizard is Copy.ai's standout feature. You enter a topic, choose a tone, and it generates a full blog post outline — then fills in each section. In our tests, it produced usable first drafts in under 5 minutes. The quality? <strong>70% publishable</strong> with minor edits.</p>

    <h3>3. Brand Voice</h3>
    <p>You can train Copy.ai to write in your brand's voice by providing sample content. After feeding it 3–5 examples, the output tone became noticeably more consistent. Not perfect, but much better than the generic AI voice most tools produce.</p>

    <h3>4. Workflows (Automation)</h3>
    <p>Copy.ai's Workflows feature lets you chain multiple AI actions together. For example: "Research topic → Generate outline → Write intro → Create social posts." This saves serious time if you're producing content at scale.</p>

    <h3>5. Chat by Copy.ai</h3>
    <p>A ChatGPT-style chatbot built into the platform. Useful for quick research, brainstorming, and getting answers. It's connected to the web, so it can pull current information — unlike ChatGPT's free tier.</p>

