    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>Is Copy.ai free?</h3>
    <p>Yes. Copy.ai offers a free plan with 2,000 words per month. No credit card required. It's enough to test all features before committing to a paid plan.</p>

    <h3>Is Copy.ai better than ChatGPT?</h3>
    <p>For marketing copy specifically, yes. Copy.ai has 90+ templates designed for ads, emails, blog posts, and social media. ChatGPT is more versatile but requires more prompting skill to get marketing-ready output.</p>

    <h3>Does Copy.ai use GPT-4?</h3>
    <p>Yes. Copy.ai uses GPT-4 and other large language models to generate content. This gives it high-quality output that's often indistinguishable from human writing.</p>

    <h3>Can Copy.ai write blog posts?</h3>
    <p>Yes. The Blog Post Wizard can generate full blog posts from a topic. In our tests, about 70% of the output was publishable with minor edits. Longer posts (2,000+ words) may need more fact-checking.</p>

    <h3>Is there a Copy.ai lifetime deal?</h3>
    <p>No. Copy.ai doesn't offer a lifetime deal as of 2026. They offer monthly and annual plans, with annual billing saving about 25%.</p>

